{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I think we have to do something"},{"time":2000,"text":"about a piece of the culture\nof medicine that has to change."},{"time":5000,"text":"And I think it starts\nwith one physician, and that's me."},{"time":8000,"text":"And maybe I've been around long enough"},{"time":10000,"text":"that I can afford to give away\nsome of my false prestige"},{"time":12691,"text":"to be able to do that."},{"time":14000,"text":"Before I actually begin\nthe meat of my talk,"},{"time":16120,"text":"let's begin with a bit of baseball."},{"time":18000,"text":"Hey, why not?"},{"time":20000,"text":"We're near the end, we're getting\nclose to the World Series."},{"time":23000,"text":"We all love baseball, don't we?"},{"time":26000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":28000,"text":"Baseball is filled\nwith some amazing statistics."},{"time":31000,"text":"And there's hundreds of them."},{"time":34000,"text":"\"Moneyball\" is about to come out,\nand it's all about statistics"},{"time":37024,"text":"and using statistics to build\na great baseball team."},{"time":39525,"text":"I'm going to focus on one stat"},{"time":42000,"text":"that I hope a lot of you have heard of."},{"time":44000,"text":"It's called batting average."},{"time":46000,"text":"So we talk about a 300,\na batter who bats 300."},{"time":49000,"text":"That means that ballplayer\nbatted safely, hit safely"},{"time":53000,"text":"three times out of 10 at bats."},{"time":56000,"text":"That means hit the ball into the outfield,"},{"time":58024,"text":"it dropped, it didn't get caught,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and whoever tried to throw it to first\nbase didn't get there in time"},{"time":63263,"text":"and the runner was safe."},{"time":65000,"text":"Three times out of 10."},{"time":68000,"text":"Do you know what they call a 300 hitter"},{"time":71000,"text":"in Major League Baseball?"},{"time":73000,"text":"Good, really good,"},{"time":76000,"text":"maybe an all-star."},{"time":79000,"text":"Do you know what they call"},{"time":81000,"text":"a 400 baseball hitter?"},{"time":83000,"text":"That's somebody who hit, by the way,"},{"time":85000,"text":"four times safely out of every 10."},{"time":87000,"text":"Legendary --"},{"time":90000,"text":"as in Ted Williams legendary --"},{"time":92000,"text":"the last Major League Baseball player"},{"time":94000,"text":"to hit over 400 during a regular season."},{"time":97000,"text":"Now let's take this back\ninto my world of medicine"},{"time":99358,"text":"where I'm a lot more comfortable,"},{"time":101000,"text":"or perhaps a bit less comfortable"},{"time":103000,"text":"after what I'm going to talk to you about."},{"time":106000,"text":"Suppose you have appendicitis"},{"time":108000,"text":"and you're referred to a surgeon"},{"time":110000,"text":"who's batting 400 on appendectomies."},{"time":112000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":115000,"text":"Somehow this isn't working out, is it?"},{"time":118000,"text":"Now suppose you live"},{"time":120000,"text":"in a certain part\nof a certain remote place"},{"time":123000,"text":"and you have a loved one"},{"time":125000,"text":"who has blockages in two coronary arteries"},{"time":128000,"text":"and your family doctor refers\nthat loved one to a cardiologist"},{"time":131000,"text":"who's batting 200 on angioplasties."},{"time":135000,"text":"But, but, you know what?"},{"time":137000,"text":"She's doing a lot better this year.\nShe's on the comeback trail."},{"time":139000,"text":"And she's hitting a 257."},{"time":142000,"text":"Somehow this isn't working."},{"time":144000,"text":"But I'm going to ask you a question."},{"time":146000,"text":"What do you think a batting average"},{"time":148000,"text":"for a cardiac surgeon\nor a nurse practitioner"},{"time":150167,"text":"or an orthopedic surgeon,"},{"time":152000,"text":"an OBGYN, a paramedic"},{"time":154000,"text":"is supposed to be?"},{"time":157000,"text":"1,000, very good."},{"time":160000,"text":"Now truth of the matter is,"},{"time":162000,"text":"nobody knows in all of medicine"},{"time":164000,"text":"what a good surgeon"},{"time":166000,"text":"or physician or paramedic"},{"time":168000,"text":"is supposed to bat."},{"time":170000,"text":"What we do though is we send\neach one of them, including myself,"},{"time":172000,"text":"out into the world"},{"time":174000,"text":"with the admonition, be perfect."},{"time":176000,"text":"Never ever, ever make a mistake,"},{"time":178000,"text":"but you worry about the details,\nabout how that's going to happen."},{"time":181167,"text":"And that was the message that I absorbed"},{"time":183167,"text":"when I was in med school."},{"time":185000,"text":"I was an obsessive compulsive student."},{"time":188000,"text":"In high school, a classmate once said"},{"time":191000,"text":"that Brian Goldman would study\nfor a blood test."},{"time":193310,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":196000,"text":"And so I did."},{"time":198000,"text":"And I studied in my little garret"},{"time":200000,"text":"at the nurses' residence\nat Toronto General Hospital,"},{"time":202548,"text":"not far from here."},{"time":204000,"text":"And I memorized everything."},{"time":206000,"text":"I memorized in my anatomy class"},{"time":208000,"text":"the origins and exertions of every muscle,"},{"time":210024,"text":"every branch of every artery\nthat came off the aorta,"},{"time":213000,"text":"differential diagnoses obscure and common."},{"time":216000,"text":"I even knew the differential diagnosis"},{"time":218000,"text":"in how to classify renal tubular acidosis."},{"time":220024,"text":"And all the while,"},{"time":222000,"text":"I was amassing more and more knowledge."},{"time":224000,"text":"And I did well, I graduated with honors,"},{"time":226000,"text":"cum laude."},{"time":228000,"text":"And I came out of medical school"},{"time":231000,"text":"with the impression"},{"time":233000,"text":"that if I memorized everything\nand knew everything,"},{"time":235453,"text":"or as much as possible,"},{"time":237000,"text":"as close to everything as possible,"},{"time":239000,"text":"that it would immunize me\nagainst making mistakes."},{"time":242000,"text":"And it worked"},{"time":244000,"text":"for a while,"},{"time":247000,"text":"until I met Mrs. Drucker."},{"time":250000,"text":"I was a resident at a teaching\nhospital here in Toronto"},{"time":252000,"text":"when Mrs. Drucker was brought\nto the emergency department"},{"time":255000,"text":"of the hospital where I was working."},{"time":257000,"text":"At the time I was assigned\nto the cardiology service"},{"time":259500,"text":"on a cardiology rotation."},{"time":261000,"text":"And it was my job,"},{"time":263000,"text":"when the emergency staff called\nfor a cardiology consult,"},{"time":265739,"text":"to see that patient in emerg."},{"time":268000,"text":"and to report back to my attending."},{"time":270000,"text":"And I saw Mrs. Drucker,\nand she was breathless."},{"time":273000,"text":"And when I listened to her,\nshe was making a wheezy sound."},{"time":276000,"text":"And when I listened to her\nchest with a stethoscope,"},{"time":278000,"text":"I could hear crackly sounds on both sides"},{"time":280000,"text":"that told me that she was in congestive\nheart failure."},{"time":283000,"text":"This is a condition\nin which the heart fails,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and instead of being able\nto pump all the blood forward,"},{"time":288000,"text":"some of the blood backs up into the lung,\nthe lungs fill up with blood,"},{"time":291000,"text":"and that's why you have\nshortness of breath."},{"time":293120,"text":"And that wasn't a difficult\ndiagnosis to make."},{"time":296000,"text":"I made it and I set to work treating her."},{"time":299000,"text":"I gave her aspirin. I gave her medications\nto relieve the strain on her heart."},{"time":302000,"text":"I gave her medications that we call\ndiuretics, water pills,"},{"time":305000,"text":"to get her to pee out the access fluid."},{"time":308000,"text":"And over the course\nof the next hour and a half or two,"},{"time":310644,"text":"she started to feel better."},{"time":312000,"text":"And I felt really good."},{"time":315000,"text":"And that's when I made my first mistake;"},{"time":318000,"text":"I sent her home."},{"time":320000,"text":"Actually, I made two more mistakes."},{"time":323000,"text":"I sent her home"},{"time":325000,"text":"without speaking to my attending."},{"time":327000,"text":"I didn't pick up the phone and do\nwhat I was supposed to do,"},{"time":330000,"text":"which was call my attending\nand run the story by him"},{"time":332501,"text":"so he would have a chance\nto see her for himself."},{"time":335000,"text":"And he knew her,"},{"time":337000,"text":"he would have been able to furnish\nadditional information about her."},{"time":340263,"text":"Maybe I did it for a good reason."},{"time":342000,"text":"Maybe I didn't want to be\na high-maintenance resident."},{"time":345000,"text":"Maybe I wanted to be so successful"},{"time":347000,"text":"and so able to take responsibility"},{"time":349000,"text":"that I would do so"},{"time":351000,"text":"and I would be able to take\ncare of my attending's patients"},{"time":353000,"text":"without even having to contact him."},{"time":355000,"text":"The second mistake that I made was worse."},{"time":359000,"text":"In sending her home,"},{"time":361000,"text":"I disregarded a little voice\ndeep down inside"},{"time":363167,"text":"that was trying to tell me,"},{"time":365000,"text":"\"Goldman, not a good idea. Don't do this.\""},{"time":368000,"text":"In fact, so lacking in confidence was I"},{"time":371000,"text":"that I actually asked the nurse"},{"time":373000,"text":"who was looking after Mrs. Drucker,"},{"time":375000,"text":"\"Do you think it's okay if she goes home?\""},{"time":378000,"text":"And the nurse thought about it"},{"time":380000,"text":"and said very matter-of-factly,\n\"Yeah, I think she'll do okay.\""},{"time":382000,"text":"I can remember that like it was yesterday."},{"time":385000,"text":"So I signed the discharge papers,"},{"time":387000,"text":"and an ambulance came, paramedics\ncame to take her home."},{"time":390000,"text":"And I went back to my work on the wards."},{"time":393000,"text":"All the rest of that day,"},{"time":395000,"text":"that afternoon,"},{"time":397000,"text":"I had this kind of gnawing\nfeeling inside my stomach."},{"time":400000,"text":"But I carried on with my work."},{"time":403000,"text":"And at the end of the day,\nI packed up to leave the hospital"},{"time":405000,"text":"and walked to the parking lot"},{"time":407000,"text":"to take my car and drive home"},{"time":409000,"text":"when I did something\nthat I don't usually do."},{"time":413000,"text":"I walked through the emergency\ndepartment on my way home."},{"time":416000,"text":"And it was there that another nurse,"},{"time":418000,"text":"not the nurse who was looking\nafter Mrs. Drucker before, but another nurse,"},{"time":421596,"text":"said three words to me"},{"time":424000,"text":"that are the three words"},{"time":426000,"text":"that most emergency\nphysicians I know dread."},{"time":429000,"text":"Others in medicine dread them as well,"},{"time":431000,"text":"but there's something particular\nabout emergency medicine"},{"time":433739,"text":"because we see patients so fleetingly."},{"time":437000,"text":"The three words are:"},{"time":439000,"text":"Do you remember?"},{"time":443000,"text":"\"Do you remember\nthat patient you sent home?\""},{"time":446000,"text":"the other nurse asked matter-of-factly."},{"time":448000,"text":"\"Well she's back,\""},{"time":450000,"text":"in just that tone of voice."},{"time":452000,"text":"Well she was back all right."},{"time":454000,"text":"She was back and near death."},{"time":457000,"text":"About an hour after she had arrived home,"},{"time":459000,"text":"after I'd sent her home,"},{"time":461000,"text":"she collapsed and her family called 911"},{"time":464000,"text":"and the paramedics brought her\nback to the emergency department"},{"time":466000,"text":"where she had a blood pressure of 50,"},{"time":468000,"text":"which is in severe shock."},{"time":470000,"text":"And she was barely breathing\nand she was blue."},{"time":473000,"text":"And the emerg. staff\npulled out all the stops."},{"time":476000,"text":"They gave her medications\nto raise her blood pressure."},{"time":479000,"text":"They put her on a ventilator."},{"time":481000,"text":"And I was shocked"},{"time":484000,"text":"and shaken to the core."},{"time":486000,"text":"And I went through this roller coaster,"},{"time":488000,"text":"because after they stabilized her,"},{"time":490000,"text":"she went to the intensive care unit,"},{"time":492000,"text":"and I hoped against hope\nthat she would recover."},{"time":494000,"text":"And over the next two or three days,"},{"time":496000,"text":"it was clear that she was never\ngoing to wake up."},{"time":498358,"text":"She had irreversible brain damage."},{"time":501000,"text":"And the family gathered."},{"time":503000,"text":"And over the course\nof the next eight or nine days,"},{"time":506000,"text":"they resigned themselves\nto what was happening."},{"time":508263,"text":"And at about the nine day\nmark, they let her go --"},{"time":511000,"text":"Mrs. Drucker,"},{"time":513000,"text":"a wife, a mother"},{"time":515000,"text":"and a grandmother."},{"time":518000,"text":"They say you never forget the names"},{"time":520000,"text":"of those who die."},{"time":522000,"text":"And that was my first time\nto be acquainted with that."},{"time":525000,"text":"Over the next few weeks,"},{"time":527000,"text":"I beat myself up"},{"time":530000,"text":"and I experienced for the first time"},{"time":532000,"text":"the unhealthy shame that exists"},{"time":534000,"text":"in our culture of medicine --"},{"time":536000,"text":"where I felt alone, isolated,"},{"time":539000,"text":"not feeling the healthy kind\nof shame that you feel,"},{"time":541000,"text":"because you can't talk\nabout it with your colleagues."},{"time":543548,"text":"You know that healthy kind,"},{"time":545000,"text":"when you betray a secret that a best\nfriend made you promise never to reveal"},{"time":548644,"text":"and then you get busted"},{"time":550000,"text":"and then your best friend confronts you"},{"time":552000,"text":"and you have terrible discussions,"},{"time":554000,"text":"but at the end of it\nall that sick feeling guides you"},{"time":557000,"text":"and you say, I'll never\nmake that mistake again."},{"time":559310,"text":"And you make amends and you\nnever make that mistake again."},{"time":562310,"text":"That's the kind of shame\nthat is a teacher."},{"time":565000,"text":"The unhealthy shame I'm talking about"},{"time":567000,"text":"is the one that makes you so sick inside."},{"time":570000,"text":"It's the one that says,"},{"time":572000,"text":"not that what you did was bad,"},{"time":574000,"text":"but that you are bad."},{"time":576000,"text":"And it was what I was feeling."},{"time":579000,"text":"And it wasn't because of my attending;\nhe was a doll."},{"time":582000,"text":"He talked to the family, and I'm quite\nsure that he smoothed things over"},{"time":585453,"text":"and made sure that I didn't get sued."},{"time":588000,"text":"And I kept asking myself these questions."},{"time":591000,"text":"Why didn't I ask my attending?\nWhy did I send her home?"},{"time":594000,"text":"And then at my worst moments:"},{"time":596000,"text":"Why did I make such a stupid mistake?"},{"time":599000,"text":"Why did I go into medicine?"},{"time":601000,"text":"Slowly but surely,"},{"time":603000,"text":"it lifted."},{"time":605000,"text":"I began to feel a bit better."},{"time":607000,"text":"And on a cloudy day,"},{"time":609000,"text":"there was a crack in the clouds\nand the sun started to come out"},{"time":611977,"text":"and I wondered,"},{"time":613000,"text":"maybe I could feel better again."},{"time":615000,"text":"And I made myself a bargain"},{"time":618000,"text":"that if only I redouble\nmy efforts to be perfect"},{"time":623000,"text":"and never make another mistake again,"},{"time":625000,"text":"please make the voices stop."},{"time":627000,"text":"And they did."},{"time":629000,"text":"And I went back to work."},{"time":631000,"text":"And then it happened again."},{"time":634000,"text":"Two years later I was an attending\nin the emergency department"},{"time":637000,"text":"at a community hospital\njust north of Toronto,"},{"time":639215,"text":"and I saw a 25 year-old\nman with a sore throat."},{"time":642000,"text":"It was busy, I was in a bit of a hurry."},{"time":644000,"text":"He kept pointing here."},{"time":646000,"text":"I looked at his throat,\nit was a little bit pink."},{"time":648358,"text":"And I gave him a prescription\nfor penicillin"},{"time":650478,"text":"and sent him on his way."},{"time":652000,"text":"And even as he was walking out the door,"},{"time":654000,"text":"he was still sort\nof pointing to his throat."},{"time":657000,"text":"And two days later I came to do\nmy next emergency shift,"},{"time":660000,"text":"and that's when my chief asked\nto speak to me quietly in her office."},{"time":663263,"text":"And she said the three words:"},{"time":667000,"text":"Do you remember?"},{"time":670000,"text":"\"Do you remember that patient\nyou saw with the sore throat?\""},{"time":673000,"text":"Well it turns out, he didn't\nhave a strep throat."},{"time":675358,"text":"He had a potentially\nlife-threatening condition"},{"time":677621,"text":"called epiglottitis."},{"time":679000,"text":"You can Google it,"},{"time":681000,"text":"but it's an infection, not\nof the throat, but of the upper airway,"},{"time":684167,"text":"and it can actually cause\nthe airway to close."},{"time":687000,"text":"And fortunately he didn't die."},{"time":690000,"text":"He was placed on intravenous antibiotics"},{"time":693000,"text":"and he recovered after a few days."},{"time":695000,"text":"And I went through the same period\nof shame and recriminations"},{"time":699000,"text":"and felt cleansed and went back to work,"},{"time":703000,"text":"until it happened again\nand again and again."},{"time":708000,"text":"Twice in one emergency shift,\nI missed appendicitis."},{"time":711000,"text":"Now that takes some doing,"},{"time":714000,"text":"especially when you work in a hospital"},{"time":716000,"text":"that at the time saw\nbut 14 people a night."},{"time":719000,"text":"Now in both cases, I didn't send them home"},{"time":722000,"text":"and I don't think there\nwas any gap in their care."},{"time":724358,"text":"One I thought had a kidney stone."},{"time":726000,"text":"I ordered a kidney X-ray. When\nit turned out to be normal,"},{"time":728000,"text":"my colleague who was doing\na reassessment of the patient"},{"time":731000,"text":"noticed some tenderness in the right\nlower quadrant and called the surgeons."},{"time":734000,"text":"The other one had a lot of diarrhea."},{"time":736000,"text":"I ordered some fluids to rehydrate him"},{"time":739000,"text":"and asked my colleague to reassess him."},{"time":742000,"text":"And he did"},{"time":744000,"text":"and when he noticed some tenderness in the right\nlower quadrant, called the surgeons."},{"time":746000,"text":"In both cases,"},{"time":748000,"text":"they had their operations\nand they did okay."},{"time":751000,"text":"But each time,"},{"time":753000,"text":"they were gnawing at me, eating at me."},{"time":755000,"text":"And I'd like to be able to say to you"},{"time":757000,"text":"that my worst mistakes only happened\nin the first five years of practice"},{"time":760453,"text":"as many of my colleagues\nsay, which is total B.S."},{"time":763000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":765000,"text":"Some of my doozies have\nbeen in the last five years."},{"time":771000,"text":"Alone, ashamed and unsupported."},{"time":773000,"text":"Here's the problem:"},{"time":775000,"text":"If I can't come clean"},{"time":777000,"text":"and talk about my mistakes,"},{"time":781000,"text":"if I can't find the still-small voice"},{"time":783000,"text":"that tells me what really happened,"},{"time":785000,"text":"how can I share it with my colleagues?"},{"time":787000,"text":"How can I teach them about what I did"},{"time":790000,"text":"so that they don't do the same thing?"},{"time":794000,"text":"If I were to walk into a room --"},{"time":796000,"text":"like right now, I have no\nidea what you think of me."},{"time":799000,"text":"When was the last time\nyou heard somebody talk"},{"time":801000,"text":"about failure after failure after failure?"},{"time":803024,"text":"Oh yeah, you go to a cocktail party"},{"time":805000,"text":"and you might hear\nabout some other doctor,"},{"time":807072,"text":"but you're not going to hear somebody"},{"time":809000,"text":"talking about their own mistakes."},{"time":811000,"text":"If I were to walk into a room\nfilled with my colleages"},{"time":814000,"text":"and ask for their support right now"},{"time":816000,"text":"and start to tell what I've just\ntold you right now,"},{"time":818453,"text":"I probably wouldn't get\nthrough two of those stories"},{"time":821000,"text":"before they would start\nto get really uncomfortable,"},{"time":823501,"text":"somebody would crack a joke,"},{"time":825000,"text":"they'd change the subject\nand we would move on."},{"time":830000,"text":"And in fact, if I knew\nand my colleagues knew"},{"time":833000,"text":"that one of my orthopedic colleagues\ntook off the wrong leg in my hospital,"},{"time":837000,"text":"believe me, I'd have trouble"},{"time":839000,"text":"making eye contact with that person."},{"time":841000,"text":"That's the system that we have."},{"time":843000,"text":"It's a complete denial of mistakes."},{"time":846000,"text":"It's a system"},{"time":848000,"text":"in which there are two kinds\nof physicians --"},{"time":852000,"text":"those who make mistakes"},{"time":854000,"text":"and those who don't,"},{"time":856000,"text":"those who can't handle sleep\ndeprivation and those who can,"},{"time":859000,"text":"those who have lousy outcomes"},{"time":861000,"text":"and those who have great outcomes."},{"time":864000,"text":"And it's almost\nlike an ideological reaction,"},{"time":866167,"text":"like the antibodies begin\nto attack that person."},{"time":870000,"text":"And we have this idea"},{"time":872000,"text":"that if we drive the people\nwho make mistakes"},{"time":874167,"text":"out of medicine,"},{"time":876000,"text":"what will we be left\nwith, but a safe system."},{"time":880000,"text":"But there are two problems with that."},{"time":883000,"text":"In my 20 years or so"},{"time":885000,"text":"of medical broadcasting and journalism,"},{"time":888000,"text":"I've made a personal study of medical\nmalpractice and medical errors"},{"time":891263,"text":"to learn everything I can,"},{"time":893000,"text":"from one of the first articles\nI wrote for the Toronto Star"},{"time":895834,"text":"to my show \"White Coat, Black Art.\""},{"time":898000,"text":"And what I've learned"},{"time":900000,"text":"is that errors are absolutely ubiquitous."},{"time":903000,"text":"We work in a system"},{"time":905000,"text":"where errors happen every day,"},{"time":907000,"text":"where one in 10 medications"},{"time":909000,"text":"are either the wrong\nmedication given in hospital"},{"time":911358,"text":"or at the wrong dosage,"},{"time":913000,"text":"where hospital-acquired infections\nare getting more and more numerous,"},{"time":916358,"text":"causing havoc and death."},{"time":919000,"text":"In this country,"},{"time":921000,"text":"as many as 24,000 Canadians die"},{"time":923000,"text":"of preventable medical errors."},{"time":925000,"text":"In the United States, the Institute\nof Medicine pegged it at 100,000."},{"time":929000,"text":"In both cases, these\nare gross underestimates,"},{"time":932000,"text":"because we really aren't\nferreting out the problem"},{"time":934405,"text":"as we should."},{"time":936000,"text":"And here's the thing."},{"time":939000,"text":"In a hospital system"},{"time":942000,"text":"where medical knowledge is doubling"},{"time":944000,"text":"every two or three years,\nwe can't keep up with it."},{"time":947000,"text":"Sleep deprivation is absolutely pervasive."},{"time":950000,"text":"We can't get rid of it."},{"time":952000,"text":"We have our cognitive biases,"},{"time":954000,"text":"so that I can take a perfect history\non a patient with chest pain."},{"time":957167,"text":"Now take the same patient with chest pain,"},{"time":959191,"text":"make them moist and garrulous"},{"time":961000,"text":"and put a little bit\nof alcohol on their breath,"},{"time":963000,"text":"and suddenly my history\nis laced with contempt."},{"time":965263,"text":"I don't take the same history."},{"time":967000,"text":"I'm not a robot;"},{"time":969000,"text":"I don't do things the same way each time."},{"time":971000,"text":"And my patients aren't cars;"},{"time":973000,"text":"they don't tell me their symptoms\nin the same way each time."},{"time":976000,"text":"Given all of that,\nmistakes are inevitable."},{"time":979000,"text":"So if you take the system,\nas I was taught,"},{"time":982000,"text":"and weed out all the error-prone\nhealth professionals,"},{"time":986000,"text":"well there won't be anybody left."},{"time":991000,"text":"And you know that business"},{"time":993000,"text":"about people not wanting"},{"time":995000,"text":"to talk about their worst cases?"},{"time":998000,"text":"On my show, on \"White Coat, Black Art,\""},{"time":1000000,"text":"I made it a habit of saying,\n\"Here's my worst mistake,\""},{"time":1002644,"text":"I would say to everybody"},{"time":1004000,"text":"from paramedics to the chief\nof cardiac surgery,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"\"Here's my worst mistake,\"\nblah, blah, blah, blah, blah,"},{"time":1009000,"text":"\"What about yours?\" and I would point\nthe microphone towards them."},{"time":1012167,"text":"And their pupils would dilate,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"they would recoil,"},{"time":1016000,"text":"then they would look down and swallow hard"},{"time":1019000,"text":"and start to tell me their stories."},{"time":1022000,"text":"They want to tell their stories.\nThey want to share their stories."},{"time":1025166,"text":"They want to be able to say,"},{"time":1027000,"text":"\"Look, don't make the same mistake I did.\""},{"time":1029023,"text":"What they need is an environment\nto be able to do that."},{"time":1031667,"text":"What they need is a redefined\nmedical culture."},{"time":1035000,"text":"And it starts\nwith one physician at a time."},{"time":1038000,"text":"The redefined physician is human,"},{"time":1041000,"text":"knows she's human,"},{"time":1043000,"text":"accepts it, isn't proud\nof making mistakes,"},{"time":1045071,"text":"but strives to learn one thing"},{"time":1047000,"text":"from what happened"},{"time":1049000,"text":"that she can teach to somebody else."},{"time":1051000,"text":"She shares her experience with others."},{"time":1053000,"text":"She's supportive when other\npeople talk about their mistakes."},{"time":1056000,"text":"And she points out other\npeople's mistakes,"},{"time":1058072,"text":"not in a gotcha way,"},{"time":1060000,"text":"but in a loving, supportive way"},{"time":1063000,"text":"so that everybody can benefit."},{"time":1065000,"text":"And she works in a culture of medicine"},{"time":1067000,"text":"that acknowledges"},{"time":1069000,"text":"that human beings run the system,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"and when human beings run the system,\nthey will make mistakes from time to time."},{"time":1074834,"text":"So the system is evolving"},{"time":1078000,"text":"to create backups"},{"time":1082000,"text":"that make it easier\nto detect those mistakes"},{"time":1085000,"text":"that humans inevitably make"},{"time":1088000,"text":"and also fosters\nin a loving, supportive way"},{"time":1091000,"text":"places where everybody who is observing"},{"time":1094000,"text":"in the health care system"},{"time":1096000,"text":"can actually point out things\nthat could be potential mistakes"},{"time":1099000,"text":"and is rewarded for doing so,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"and especially people like me,\nwhen we do make mistakes,"},{"time":1103691,"text":"we're rewarded for coming clean."},{"time":1107000,"text":"My name is Brian Goldman."},{"time":1110000,"text":"I am a redefined physician."},{"time":1113000,"text":"I'm human. I make mistakes."},{"time":1115000,"text":"I'm sorry about that,"},{"time":1117000,"text":"but I strive to learn one thing"},{"time":1119000,"text":"that I can pass on to other people."},{"time":1122000,"text":"I still don't know what you think of me,"},{"time":1125000,"text":"but I can live with that."},{"time":1127000,"text":"And let me close\nwith three words of my own:"},{"time":1130000,"text":"I do remember."},{"time":1134000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}